snippet.title: Evil Dead: The Game - Kandarian Demon Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Command vicious Deadites, set diabolical traps, possess survivors and swallow some souls!

Check out the new Kandarian Demon gameplay trailer, narrated by the one and only Bruce Campbell himself

EVIL DEAD: THE GAME is coming May 13
